20
00:03:09,310 --> 00:03:10,280
Why are you here?

21
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:12,430
We're sisters.

22
00:03:12,630 --> 00:03:13,840
I'm here to see you.

23
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:16,430
However,

24
00:03:17,030 --> 00:03:18,710
should I call you Meng Li

25
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:20,750
or Shang You?

26
00:03:22,590 --> 00:03:24,750
Shang You, Saint of Holy Spirits,

27
00:03:24,870 --> 00:03:26,840
why did you pretend to be a deer monster

28
00:03:27,150 --> 00:03:28,520
to infiltrate us?

29
00:03:35,430 --> 00:03:36,750
Soul Devouring Spike!

30
00:03:37,190 --> 00:03:38,520
Break her spiritual roots

31
00:03:38,910 --> 00:03:40,710
and destory her soul.

32
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:11,800
Your Majesty!

33
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:13,280
She's mine.

34
00:04:13,750 --> 00:04:15,000
No one

35
00:04:15,430 --> 00:04:16,680
can touch her except for me.

36
00:04:18,310 --> 00:04:20,240
I told her to do it.

37
00:04:20,830 --> 00:04:21,670
Mother,

38
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:23,270
