41
00:04:26,750 --> 00:04:28,310
She's not a deer monster

42
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:30,270
but Shang You, the saint

43
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:31,320
of holy spirits.

44
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:35,390
This is Reminiscence Mirror,

45
00:04:35,950 --> 00:04:37,000
the heirloom of holy spirits.

46
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:43,920
In the presence of God,

47
00:04:44,070 --> 00:04:45,510
we promise to stay together forever

48
00:04:45,750 --> 00:04:47,040
till death do us part.

49
00:04:49,390 --> 00:04:50,240
She married

50
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:51,890
Jiang Ziheng,
the eldest disciple of the Yuxu Sect,

51
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:53,070
